code: protected Endpoint createEndpoint(String uri, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     GrpcConfiguration config = new GrpcConfiguration().     config = parseConfiguration(config, uri, parameters).     setProperties(config, parameters).     Endpoint endpoint = new GrpcEndpoint(uri, this, config).     return endpoint. }

comment: /**  * Parses the configuration  *  * @return the parsed and valid configuration to use  */
code: /**  * Parses the configuration  *  * @return the parsed and valid configuration to use  */ protected GrpcConfiguration parseConfiguration(GrpcConfiguration configuration, String remaining, Map<String, Object> parameters) throws Exception {     configuration.parseURI(new URI(remaining), parameters, this).     return configuration. }
